claude-code-viewer — Browse any codebase with an AI-powered web UI.

Usage:
    claude-code-viewer                # serve current directory
    claude-code-viewer /path/to/repo  # serve specific project
    claude-code-viewer --port 3000    # custom port

Features:
    - Auto-scans project structure and renders an interactive site
    - Chat widget: ask Claude Code about the codebase from the browser
    - Right-click any selected text → "Ask Claude Code"
    - Suggested prompts per detected component
    - No dependencies beyond Python 3.8+ and `claude` CLI
"""
